{"tid":1220824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警海富中心天橋截查行人 宗教人士中信天橋唱詩歌","createTime":"2019-06-14T05:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T05:36:08.000Z","uid":241764,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee0b636e14804e5c57a03a13a25b957584d3e35","tid":1220824,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"2019-06-14 11:41<br />\n因應政府準備修訂《逃犯條例》，金鐘前日爆發大規模警民衝突後，附近一帶今日雖然氣氛平靜，但警方仍在場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n警員在連接政府總部的海富中心天橋上把守，並截查行人；另有約10名宗教人士，早上到附近的中信大廈天橋，隔著鐵馬向在場駐守的警員高唱詩歌。<br />\n<br />\n中午前，一名紅衣男子在中信大廈天橋上，激動地指罵記者扇風點火，被警員帶離現場，期間再與女途人發生口角。"},{"pid":"0f1d6a25f7a751e2adfe9e7f388b4d6aa9130ec6","tid":1220824,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一日淋病唔撤回 一日都未成功！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"92f7d55fb3e0cbd05cfac0e2a298728971955e9e","tid":1220824,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1022797-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%B5%B7%E5%AF%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA+%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E5%94%B1%E8%A9%A9%E6%AD%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1022797-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25AF%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%259F%25A5%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%2B%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B%25E5%2594%25B1%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E6%25AD%258C&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWBZZVu6JdVYNpUv